{
  "stem": "3984.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when I was, when I was-- when we, when we finish, when we was free, I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And took me to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I was-- I think I was-- I don't know how long, in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At the hospital, they take me to a special place where is only children-- a lot of children from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They collect a lot of children, because they have lots of children without parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my mother-- I know that my mother and sisters was in ghetto, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I know that they are over there, and we are free.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I get all kind of medicine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And later, when I get a little better, they took me-- together with a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We was in Budapest, I don't know how long, because everything-- it was very short time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, we have, over there, teachers take care of us, and start to be not teach us-- only, you know, to give us music, and to dance with us, to give us very good food, to tell us stories, because we was very young.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was all kind of ages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was more-- it was children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was more bigger, like me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they was very little and skinny, so nobody can know what is their ages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they collect us, and they collect from all the world ten hundred-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--together.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they take us to German, to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but they know that I left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They know that I went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They know-- of course, this is, this is free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told us that they-- we came to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
